Sentencas: Steady generation of electricity with dry CH4 fuel, 150 mW center dot cm(-2) at 1073 K and 360 mW center dot cm(-2) at 1173 K, was successfully performed by a low loading of Pd-Ni bimetallic catalyst on a lanthanum chromite based porous-composite anode for solid oxide fuel cells (SOFC).
Titulo: Direct oxidation of methane by Pd-Ni bimetallic catalyst over lanthanum chromite based anode for SOFC

Sentencas: The amounts of carbon deposition were quite small under the open and closed circuit conditions.
Titulo: Direct oxidation of methane by Pd-Ni bimetallic catalyst over lanthanum chromite based anode for SOFC

Sentencas: The electrocatalytic activity of the Pd-Ni catalyst was significantly higher than that of Pd or Ni catalysts.
Titulo: Direct oxidation of methane by Pd-Ni bimetallic catalyst over lanthanum chromite based anode for SOFC
